    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's a debate, but like, if a gov has to pick one to focus on first because they can't do both perfectly, which one is actually the more \"responsible\" choice for the long-term health of the country? is it better to be fiscally disciplined or to protect the people?",
      "source": "evaluator"
