      "content": "that seems kind of harsh though. what about when people are actually suffering right now? isn't it kind of irresponsible to let people fall into poverty or lose healthcare just to balance a budget for future generations? doesn't that make the \"fiscally disciplined\" approach actually pretty harmful in the short term?",
